## More I've built

<sub>Everything else I build and maintain, beyond the flagships above — my own agents, tools, and products, most of them open source.</sub>

#### AI agents & tooling

<table>
  <colgroup>
    <col style="width:120px">
    <col style="width:200px">
    <col>
  </colgroup>
{{#each _aiAgentProjects}}  <tr>
    <td>{{#if logo}}<img src="{{logo}}" height="72" alt="{{name}}" title="{{name}}">{{else}}&nbsp;{{/if}}</td>
    <td><strong><a href="{{default url repoUrl}}">{{briefTagline name}}</a></strong>{{#if _contextLogo.length}}<br><sub>{{#each _contextLogo}}<a href="{{url}}"><img src="{{src}}" height="20" alt="{{alt}}"></a>{{#unless @last}} {{/unless}}{{/each}}</sub>{{/if}}</td>
    <td>{{#if narrative.impactHeadline}}<em>{{narrative.impactHeadline}}</em>{{else}}{{briefTagline tagline}}{{/if}}{{#if _clientOrg}}<br><sub>↳ Part of <a href="{{_clientOrg.url}}">{{_clientOrg.name}}</a></sub>{{/if}}{{#if _relatedProjectsResolved.length}}<br><sub>↳ Related: {{#each _relatedProjectsResolved}}<a href="{{default url repoUrl}}">{{briefTagline name}}</a>{{#unless @last}} · {{/unless}}{{/each}}</sub>{{/if}}</td>
  </tr>
{{/each}}</table>

